"Las sillas por <strong>API key</strong> (Anthropic / OpenAI-compatible / OpenRouter)\n"
"            hablan directo con el proveedor, sin CLI. Las keys se guardan <strong>cifradas con tu\n"
"            passphrase</strong> en <code>data/secrets.enc</code>: si se pierde el pendrive sin la passphrase,\n"
"            no hay tokens en claro."
msgstr ""
"Seats by <strong>API key</strong> (Anthropic / OpenAI-compatible / "
"OpenRouter) talk straight to the provider, no CLI. Keys are stored "
"<strong>encrypted with your passphrase</strong> in "
"<code>data/secrets.enc</code>: if the stick is lost without the passphrase, "
"there are no plaintext tokens."

