"La passphrase nunca se guarda ni se loguea; se usa solo para cifrar y "
"descifrar tus keys."
msgstr ""
"The passphrase is never stored nor logged; it’s only used to encrypt and "
"decrypt your keys."

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/conexiones.html:204
msgid ""
"Con el toolbelt <strong>encendido</strong>, las sillas por API key dejan de solo conversar\n"
"            y pueden <strong>inspeccionar y operar la computadora donde corre Swarm</strong> (la del cliente). Es el\n"
"            corazón del soporte: la silla mira el sistema <strong>real</strong> en vez de adivinar."
msgstr ""
"With the toolbelt <strong>on</strong>, API-key seats stop just chatting and "
"can <strong>inspect and operate the computer where Swarm runs</strong> (the "
"client’s). It’s the heart of support work: the seat looks at the "
"<strong>real</strong> system instead of guessing."

