#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/mesa.html:359
msgid ""
"En modo Líder, el líder descompone tu pedido en subtareas, se las reparte a las\n"
"                            otras sillas y al final integra todo. Con <code>@silla</code> hablás directo a una."
msgstr ""
"In Leader mode, the leader breaks your request into subtasks, hands them out"
" to the other seats and integrates everything at the end. With "
"<code>@seat</code> you talk straight to one."

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/mesa.html:363
msgid "Tope de gasto (USD)"
msgstr "Spend cap (USD)"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/mesa.html:366
msgid "0 = sin tope"
msgstr "0 = no cap"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/mesa.html:369
msgid ""
"En modo continuo, si el gasto estimado acumulado supera el tope, la mesa no\n"
"                            corre la próxima iteración. <strong>0 = sin tope.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"In continuous mode, if the accumulated estimated spend exceeds the cap, the "
"table will not run the next iteration. <strong>0 = no cap.</strong>"

#: enjambre/templates/enjambre/mesa.html:378
